    "asOf": "2021-02-11",
    "date": "2021-03-15T16:33:11Z",
    "text": "This bill extends for two years the election and capital gain deferral periods for qualified opportunity zones. An opportunity zone is an economically-distressed community where private investments, under certain conditions, may be eligible for capital gain tax incentives."
